Life has a funny way of moving way too fast when we're having a good time and way too slow when we're trying to reach our biggest goals. It's all a matter of perception. All too often we compare our Chapter One to someones Chapter 25 and become frustrated because hard work and patience isn't a whole lot of fun sometimes. When we shift our way of thinking and only focus on becoming a better version of ourselves each day we instantly see a fast track to progress. When you focus on the man in the mirror and not everyone else you gain focus and self awareness. Just ask @kizmvp who is continuously striving to push himself out of his comfort zone in order to achieve greatness and have a positive impact on the world.
